rows.label: tlk42300061_02_msg0001
rows.name:
It's great, mo! A direct route
from Avaritia to Yeshiva Harbor
has been established, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300061_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Thanks to that, sending
letters and cooking has
become incomparably faster, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300061_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard it was Rex who set
up the regular service, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300061_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Sending money and setting up regular service...
You're the finest person Kurukuru has ever seen,
mo! I must learn from your example, mo!
